#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:228
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\subsection*{Gained Stacked Units}\n"
"  Some rewards allow you to gain a Stacked Creature Bank unit card.\n"
"  Track which of your units are Stacked by whatever means is comfortable, e.g.~by remembering it or by placing a Token or Cube on it.\n"
"  Whenever your Stacked unit goes to a Combat, draw a random Stack Token and place it on that unit.\n"
"  After Combat, note whether the unit is still Stacked (for future Combats), then return the Stack Token to the pile.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\subsection*{Zdobywanie Ulepszonych Jednostek}\n"
"  W niektórych Bankach Stworzeń w ramach nagrody możesz zdobyć Ulepszoną Jednostkę.\n"
"  Taką jednostkę również będziesz oznaczać żetonem Ulepszonej Jednostki, który będziesz losować za każdym razem, gdy wystawisz ją do Walki.\n"
"  Po walce zaznacz, która jednostka jest wciąż Ulepszona (dla celów przyszłych Walk) i zwróć Żeton Ulepszonej Jednostki do stosu.\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:232
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\begin{center}\n"
"    \\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=\\iftoggle{printable}{0.9}{0.8}\\linewidth]{\\art/frost_ring.png}\n"
"  \\end{center}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\begin{center}\n"
"    \\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=\\iftoggle{printable}{0.9}{0.8}\\linewidth]{\\art/frost_ring.png}\n"
"  \\end{center}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:234
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\end{expansion}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\end{expansion}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:240
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\columnbreak\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Alternative Combat Boards}{\\subheader{Alternative Combat Boards}}\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}{navalbattles}\\index{Naval Battle}\n"
"  As an \\textbf{optional rule}, you can use the \\textbf{Naval Battle Board} for combats at sea locations.\n"
"  This Board removes the two middle spaces, requiring Ground \\svg{unit_ground} units to navigate around them while Flying \\svg{unit_flying} units can move over them but cannot end their movement there.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\columnbreak\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Alternative Combat Boards}{\\subheader{Alternatywne Plansze Walki}}\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}{navalbattles}\\index{Naval Battle}\n"
"  \\textbf{Opcjonalnie} możesz użyć \\textbf{planszy Walki Morskiej} w czasie walki na kafelkach morza.\n"
"  Na Planszy tej brakuje dwóch centralnych pól, wymaga to od jednostek Naziemnych \\svg{unit_ground} omijania ich. Z kolei jednostki Latające \\svg{unit_flying} mogą nad nimi przelatywać, ale nie mogą się na nich zatrzymać.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:245
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\begin{center}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.05\\linewidth]{\\images/naval_combat.png}\n"
"  \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{expansion}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\begin{center}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.05\\linewidth]{\\images/naval_combat.png}\n"
"  \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{expansion}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:251
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\vspace{2em}\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}{battlefield}\n"
"  As an \\textbf{optional rule}, you can use the \\textbf{Battlefield Board} for combats between players in regular games.\n"
"  You can also use it for Neutral Combats, though this is not recommended.\n"
"  Refer to the \\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{Battlefield section} for the rule changes regarding this Combat type.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\vspace{2em}\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}{battlefield}\n"
"  \\textbf{Opcjonalnie} możesz użyć \\textbf{planszy Pola Bitwy} podczas walki między graczami w innych trybach gry.\n"
"  Możesz również używać jej do w czasie walk z Jednostkami Neutralnymi, ale jest to odradzane.\n"
"  Sprawdź \\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{sekcję zasad Pola Bitwy} w celu zapoznania się z zasadami walki w tym trybie.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:257
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\begin{center}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.05\\linewidth]{\\images/battlefield-board.png}\n"
"  \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{expansion}"
msgstr ""
"  \\begin{center}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.05\\linewidth]{\\images/battlefield-board.png}\n"
"  \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{expansion}"

